int _GET_VEHICLE_ROOF_LIVERY_COUNT(Vehicle vehicle);Parameters:vehicle: The vehicle handle.Returns: A number of available rooftop liveries for vehicle.Returns a number of available rooftop liveries, or -1 if vehicle has no rooftop liveries available.
